    "Html": "On my DataGrid I have a ComboBox column.  I handle its SelectionChanged event to update the value of two text columns so the user can see the new values before the row is commited.  This worked fine in the January release, but now with the March 21st release the columns aren't being updated when UpdateTarget() is called.  Is there anything that I've overlooked?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">private</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\"> <span style=\"color:blue\">void</span> cboType_SelectionChanged(<span style=\"color:blue\">object</span> sender, <span style=\"color:#2b91af\">SelectionChangedEventArgs</span> e)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\">{</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#2b91af;font-size:8pt\">DataGridRow</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\"> row = (<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">DataGridRow)</span>dataGrid.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex(dataGrid.SelectedIndex);</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#2b91af;font-size:8pt\">DataGridColumn</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\"> columnBasedOn = dataGrid.Columns.Where(c =&gt; c.Header.ToString() == <span style=\"color:#a31515\">&quot;Based On&quot;</span>).First();</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#2b91af;font-size:8pt\">DataGridColumn</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\"> columnAmount = dataGrid.Columns.Where(c =&gt; c.Header.ToString() == <span style=\"color:#a31515\">&quot;Amount&quot;</span>).First();</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\"> </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\">columnBasedOn.GetCellContent(row).GetBindingExpression(<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">TextBlock</span>.TextProperty).UpdateTarget();            <br>\r\ncolumnAmount.GetCellContent(row).GetBindingExpression(<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">TextBlock</span>.TextProperty).UpdateTarget();</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 6pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\">}</span></p>\r\n",
