    "Id": "172361",
    "ThreadId": "51264",
    "Html": "Sorry, I think I understand my problem better now.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe combobox is bound to a property of the data record which determines the value of the two other columns.  In the January release, when the selected item in the combobox changes, the property it's binding to is immediately updated.  In the March release the propery is updated after the combobox loses focus.  The UpdateSourceTrigger for the combobox column's binding is set to PropertyChanged, so I'm confused.  I tested this out by uninstalling the March release and installing January's and, without changing any code, the behaviour changed.  <br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks for bearing with me.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">toolkit</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">:</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">DataGridComboBoxColumn</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Header</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;Fee Type&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\">ItemsSource</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Source</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">={</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">StaticResource</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> feetypesDataProvider</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">}}&quot;<span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';font-size:8pt\"><span style=\"color:red\">DisplayMemberPath</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;Name&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\"> SelectedValueBinding</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:red\"> Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=FeeTypeID,</span><span style=\"color:red\"> Mode</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=TwoWay,</span><span style=\"color:red\"> UpdateSourceTrigger</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=PropertyChanged}&quot; </span><span style=\"color:red\">SelectedValuePath</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;RecordID&quot;&gt;</span>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">toolkit</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">:</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">DataGridComboBoxColumn.EditingElementStyle</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">        &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">Style</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> TargetType</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;ComboBox&quot;&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">            &lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">EventSetter</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Event</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;SelectionChanged&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Handler</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;cboType_SelectionChanged&quot;/&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">        &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">Style</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">toolkit</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">:</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">DataGridComboBoxColumn.EditingElementStyle</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">toolkit</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">:</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">DataGridComboBoxColumn</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:normal;margin:0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">toolkit</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">:</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">DataGridTextColumn</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Header</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;Based On&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> IsReadOnly</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;True&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Binding</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=FeeType.BasedOn}&quot;/&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 6pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">&lt;</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">toolkit</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">:</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">DataGridTextColumn</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\">Header</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;Amount&quot;</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Binding</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">Binding</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Path</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=Amount,</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Converter</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">={</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:#a31515;font-size:8pt\">StaticResource</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> MoneyConverter</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">},</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:red;font-size:8pt\"> Mode</span><span style=\"line-height:115%;font-family:'courier new';color:blue;font-size:8pt\">=TwoWay}&quot;/&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
